<p>Thanks CD for <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>.</p>  
<p>Sends a copy of his <hi rend="italic">oratio inauguralis</hi> on <hi rend="italic">De harmonie van het dierlijke leven</hi> [1848] in which he espoused evolution, but did not see the influence of natural selection.</p> 
